Class MyTunes

  • java.lang.Object
    • example.MyTunes

  • public class MyTunes
extends java.lang.Object
    One object of class MyTunes parses a CSV file. Each row is stored as an entry in an array of MP3 objects. Includes main() for debugging.
    Author:
    Foothill College, Bita M

      • readSongs

        private java.lang.String[][] readSongs(java.lang.String filename)
        Reads a CSV file and creates a 2D array of strings with the properties of all songs. Format of file is: ROWS value COLS value title,artist,genre,year title,artist,genre,year etc.
        Parameters:
        filename - Name of the input CSV file.
        Returns:
        2D array of strings with the properties of each song
